  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Social Media Manager/Retoiucher at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc."
      subtitle="From August 08, 2023 to [End Date] at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc., Cabanatuan City, Philippines."
    >
    I manage the social media pages in this company, where I create and edit images to be posted in our social media pages, I also manage the ADS in the Facebook Page.
