    <TimeLineElement
      title="Support Service Engineer at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc."
      subtitle="From August 08, 2023 to [End Date] at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc., Cabanatuan City, Philippines."
    >
    I also worked here as a support service engineer or a technician. Specifically, I know how to repair units such as printers,laptop, POS, etc. but with limited knowledge only.
