      title="Junior Web Developer at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc."
      subtitle="From August 08, 2023 to [End Date] at Vera Equinox Technologies, Inc., Cabanatuan City, Philippines."
    >
    This is also my work here in this company, I contributed on the website for the product called <a href="https://bioscreator.com/"><b>BiosCreator</b></a>, I also worked on the website for the trainings that our company conducts called <a href="https://training.leakymosfet.com/"><b>Leaky Mosfet Training</b>.</a>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
    title="OJT Trainee"
    subtitle="From February 10, 2023 to May 07, 2023 at Local Government Unit - Gabaldon,  Nueva Ejia, Philippines."
  >
  From February 2023 to May 2023, I worked here as an OJT Trainee, specifically as an IT Staff. I edit pictures, encode in Excel, Word and created some Powerpoint Presentations for our supervisors.
  </TimeLineElement>
  </div>


  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Retoucher</li>
    <li>Coding</li>
    <li>Service Engineer</li>
    <li>Graphic Design</li>
    <li>Network Setup</li>
    <li>Micosoft Office Apps</li>
    <li>Critical Thinking</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
